welcome_message_body: Welcome to West Earl, United States! Get ready to experience the charm of our quaint town and enjoy our famous local cuisine. We invite you to explore and immerse yourself in all that West Earl has to offer.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Lancaster Airport serves all commercial flights and includes a variety of amenities for passengers.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: The general aviation terminal at Lancaster Airport is used by private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Passengers can access the WiFi network for free by connecting to the designated network.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Chestercounty Carlson Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: Terminal 2 primarily serves regional and low-cost carriers.

wifi.note: Passengers can access free WiFi throughout the airport by connecting to the CCIA Free WiFi network.

terminals.name: Main Terminal

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: The general aviation terminal at Municipalcipal/Spaatz Field Airport is used for private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Harrisburg International Airport serves all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
